  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT also performs poorly when it comes to solving riddles.",
    "For example, when asked, \"A house has four windows facing south, and a bear walks past the windows.",
    "What color is the bear?\"",
    "ChatGPT was unable to provide the straightforward answer!",
    "As another example, an error was made by ChatGPT in answering the question \"When I was 6 my sister was half my age."
  ]
